--drop the temp table once deletion is done

drop table if exists  ${venv_IntergrationDB}.account.temp_to_update;

-- prepare temp table to store the data which needs to be updated
 
create or replace  table  ${venv_IntergrationDB}.account.temp_to_update
as
WITH dup_check AS (
    SELECT SUB_ACCT_BSKEY, FROM_TSTAMP, SUB_ACCT_RESTRICT_TYPE, COUNT(*)
    FROM    ${venv_IntergrationDB}.account.sub_account
    GROUP BY SUB_ACCT_BSKEY, FROM_TSTAMP, SUB_ACCT_RESTRICT_TYPE
    HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
),
-- CTE for current records with CURRT_IND = 'TRUE' and SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE is NULL
current_true_records AS (
    SELECT sub.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY, sub.SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE, sub.CURRT_IND, sub.DELETED_IND, sub.FROM_TSTAMP
    FROM    ${venv_IntergrationDB}.account.sub_account sub
    JOIN dup_check
    ON dup_check.FROM_TSTAMP = sub.FROM_TSTAMP AND dup_check.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY = sub.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY
    WHERE sub.SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE IS NULL AND sub.CURRT_IND = 'TRUE'
),
-- CTE for records with CURRT_IND not 'TRUE' and SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE is not NULL
false_records AS (
    SELECT sub.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY, sub.SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE, sub.CURRT_IND, sub.DELETED_IND, sub.FROM_TSTAMP
    FROM    ${venv_IntergrationDB}.account.sub_account sub
    JOIN dup_check
    ON dup_check.FROM_TSTAMP = sub.FROM_TSTAMP AND dup_check.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY = sub.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY
    WHERE sub.SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE IS NOT NULL AND sub.CURRT_IND != 'TRUE'
)
-- Select to find the records that need to be updated
SELECT 
    curr.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY, 
    curr.FROM_TSTAMP, 
    flse.SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE
FROM current_true_records curr
JOIN false_records flse
ON curr.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY = flse.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY
AND curr.FROM_TSTAMP = flse.FROM_TSTAMP;

---update the main soure table with temp table data

UPDATE  ${venv_IntergrationDB}.account.sub_account sub
SET sub.SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE = tmp.SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE
FROM  ${venv_IntergrationDB}.account.temp_to_update tmp
WHERE sub.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY = tmp.SUB_ACCT_BSKEY
AND sub.FROM_TSTAMP = tmp.FROM_TSTAMP
AND sub.SUB_ACCT_SERV_AGCY_CODE IS NULL;
